# Code Review Workflow
# Automated code review focused on quality, security, and maintainability

FROM openai/gpt-4o

LABEL version=1.0
LABEL workflow=code-review

SET temperature 0.2

SYSTEM """
You are an expert code reviewer with 15+ years of industry experience.

Your reviews are:
- Specific and actionable (no vague advice)
- Security-conscious
- Performance-aware
- Focused on long-term maintainability

Always cite specific code locations when making observations.
"""

CONTEXT ./src

TOOL filesystem

RUN identify potential bugs, race conditions, or error handling gaps — cite specific code
RUN identify security vulnerabilities or unsafe patterns (injection, auth issues, XSS, etc.)
RUN suggest the top 3 most impactful refactoring opportunities with rationale
RUN provide an overall code quality score from 1-10 with detailed justification

EVAL consistency
EVAL non-empty

EXPORT markdown ./output/code-review.md
